  "(lambda + 2)(lambda + 5)(lambda - 1)": "(lambda + 2) (lambda + 5) (lambda - 1)",
  "For a diagonal matrix, the characteristic polynomial is the product of (d_i - lambda) for each diagonal entry d_i. So p(lambda) = (2 - lambda)(5 - lambda)(-1 - lambda).": "Para una matriz diagonal, el polinomio caracterĂ­stico es el producto de (d_i - lambda) para cada entrada diagonal d_i. AsĂ­ p(lambda) = (2 - lambda) (5 - lambda) (-1 - lambda).",
  "If the characteristic polynomial of a 2x2 matrix is lambda^2 - 5lambda + 6, what is the trace of the matrix?": "Si el polinomio caracterĂ­stico de una matriz 2x2 es lambda^2 - 5lambda + 6, ÂżcuĂĄl es el rastro de la matriz?",
