  "For I = [[1,0],[0,1]], det(I - lambda I) = (1-lambda)^2 = (lambda-1)^2. The only eigenvalue is 1 with algebraic multiplicity 2.": "Para I = [[1,0],[0,1], det(I - lambda I) = (1-lambda)^2 = (lambda-1)^2. El Ăşnico valor propio es 1 con multiplicidad algebraica 2.",
  "For a triangular matrix with diagonal entries 3, -2, and 7, what are the roots of the characteristic polynomial?": "Para una matriz triangular con entradas diagonales 3, -2 y 7, ÂżcuĂĄles son las raĂ­ces del polinomio caracterĂ­stico?",
