  "The rank of A": "El rango de A",
  "The norm of A": "La norma de A",
  "The trace of A": "El rastro de A",
  "Evaluating the characteristic polynomial at lambda = 0 gives det(A - 0*I) = det(A). Therefore, the constant term equals the determinant of A.": "Evaluar el polinomio caracterĂ­stico en lambda = 0 da det(A - 0*I) = det(A). Por lo tanto, el tĂŠrmino constante es igual al determinante de A.",
  "Find the characteristic polynomial of A = [[0, -1], [1, 0]].": "Encontrar el polinomio caracterĂ­stico de A = [[0, -1], [1, 0]].",
