  "(-1/10)(A + 7I)": "(-1/10)(A + 7I)",
  "By Cayley-Hamilton, A^2 + 7A + 10I = 0. Multiplying both sides by A^(-1): A + 7I + 10A^(-1) = 0, so A^(-1) = (-1/10)(A + 7I).": "Por Cayley-Hamilton, A^2 + 7A + 10I = 0. Multiplicando ambos lados por A^(-1): A + 7I + 10A^(-1) = 0, asĂ­ que A^(-1) = (-1/10)(A + 7I).",
  "A quantum computing researcher works with the Pauli-Z matrix Z = [[1, 0], [0, -1]]. What is the characteristic polynomial of Z?": "Un investigador de computaciĂłn cuĂĄntica trabaja con la matriz Pauli-Z Z = [[1, 0], [0, -1]]. ÂżCuĂĄl es el polinomio caracterĂ­stico de Z?",
  "lambda^2 + 2lambda + 1": "lambda^2 + 2lambda + 1",
