  "A financial analyst models portfolio risk with the covariance matrix S = [[9, 3, 0], [3, 5, 1], [0, 1, 2]]. What is the sum of all eigenvalues of S?": "Un analista financiero modela el riesgo de cartera con la matriz de covarianza S = [[9, 3, 0], [3, 5, 1], [0, 1, 2]]. ÂżCuĂĄl es la suma de todos los valores propios de S?",
