  "An electrical engineer designs a filter described by the transfer matrix H = [[2, -1], [1, 4]]. To determine the system's poles, she finds the characteristic polynomial. What is it?": "Un ingeniero elĂŠctrico diseĂąa un filtro descrito por la matriz de transferencia H = [[2, -1], [1, 4]]. Para determinar los polos del sistema, encuentra el polinomio caracterĂ­stico. ÂżQuĂŠ es?",
